{"tid":440154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大研究發現病人服薑黃 炎症性腸病有改善","createTime":"2017-10-18T13:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-18T14:09:58.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1635cf12a0804b2e4d889273d856bf72436ae66d","tid":440154,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"病人服薑黃 腸炎病情有改善<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1925000/1927536/yyyy1017086_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1925000%2F1927536%2Fyyyy1017086_1024.jpg&h=20b8aab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n炎症性腸病暫時無藥可醫，但中大醫學院發現，部分病人服食薑黃後，腸炎病情有改善，冀研製成丸裝藥物，方便病人服用。<br />\n<br />\n薑黃是常用中藥的一種，中大醫學院內科及藥物治療學系教授黃秀娟教授指出，有研究發現薑黃根部提煉的補充劑或對炎症性腸病有療效。薑黃有抗發炎及抗癌作用，有病人因傳統療法無效，服用薑黃補充劑後病情有改善，但相關原理未明。研究團隊補充，目前市售薑黃補充劑藥理數據不多，中大會自行研究薑黃劑量及服用次數對病情的影響，最終希望能製成丸狀藥物，方便病人服用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全球研究人員近年不斷發掘薑黃的藥用價值。台灣中研院去年公布研究成果，指透過老鼠對照實驗，發現薑黃內含有多羥基薑黃素衍生物，有助刺激增進人腦內的腦啡肽酶（NEP）酵素活性，有望進而用於預防阿茲海默症。另外，日本京都醫療中心亦發現薑黃內的薑黃色素，對治療關節炎有止痛有功效，令患者減少服用止痛藥。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/1927536/%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%8D%E8%96%91%E9%BB%83%20%20%20%E8%85%B8%E7%82%8E%E7%97%85%E6%83%85%E6%9C%89%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1927536%2F%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259C%258D%25E8%2596%2591%25E9%25BB%2583%2520%2520%2520%25E8%2585%25B8%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%2596%2584&d=9BZZCRCLOdbvgYblKvxMCf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=deb90f33\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/1927536/%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%8D%E8%96%91%E9%BB%83%20%20%20%E8%85%B8%E7%82%8E%E7%97%85%E6%83%85%E6%9C%89%E6%94%B9%E5%96%84</a>"},{"pid":"b94b3e6a8425e5e3c7b9e6a4fdc5c0132a5287be","tid":440154,"uid":49730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:25:19.000Z","msg":"中醫"},{"pid":"8df12f2d27be45d5a0106b60f0d3cb6fc00cdb5d","tid":440154,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:39:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f3096d9b1a47a48cc017729f651e5b0b00b57cf","tid":440154,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"一早知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e105f53615392b3f2c7edee40c46cad947102b","tid":440154,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:01:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">部分病人</span>服食薑黃後，腸炎病情有改善<br />\n<br />\n其他服食薑黃的病人呢?"},{"pid":"7124d37c2c552eb3518697c99118ab1ae89d0cc6","tid":440154,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:05:53.000Z","msg":"//服用薑黃補充劑後病情有改善，但相關原理未明//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實食薄荷都有咁既功能，不過都係原理未明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0d926e91bcf2362fa7dd0582db0a42d5e53b2f","tid":440154,"uid":58005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T14:09:58.000Z","msg":"食turmeric 好似對成個身體都好多益處, 早排買左成KG應該有排食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}